The paper discusses the vulnerability of Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) to adversarial examples and proposes a method to enhance steganalysis features for detecting such examples. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Computer Security (cs.CR), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Among these, cs.CR and cs.CV are the most likely categories as the paper deals with security and image analysis. The other categories are also possible as the paper involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques.
